{"id":27840863069,"name":"Run api tests","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAGe3HbXQ","head_branch":"perf-getmetadata-oug-member-count","head_sha":"90f207d397ab032c676106230d6901c4ddf1dddc","path":".github/workflows/run-api-tests.yml","run_number":50646,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"perf: avoid loading org unit group members for OUG{} indicator counts","status":"completed","conclusion":"cancelled","workflow_id":5591308,"check_suite_id":75038353348,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAAReKJnxA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27840863069","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27840863069","pull_requests":[{"id":3900221191,"number":24260,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/24260","head":{"ref":"perf-getmetadata-oug-member-count","sha":"34d1e923bbeaf71df0df564d8a2b6aba656bf2ab","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"master","sha":"7ba24318380b8459ee61966e00a4860857c43f49","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-06-19T17:53:17Z","updated_at":"2026-06-19T18:02:45Z","run_started_at":"2026-06-19T17:53:17Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27840863069/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27840863069/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/75038353348","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27840863069/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27840863069/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27840863069/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"perf: avoid loading org unit group members for OUG{} indicator counts\n\nsubstituteIndicatorExpressions (called on every dhis-web-dataentry getMetaData request) resolved each OUG{uid} indicator reference via group.getMembers().size(), which initialises the entire org unit group members collection - on a large instance, 70k+ OrganisationUnit entities hydrated into the session per request.\n\nThis dominated getMetaData: a ~5s floor and spikes to 14-22s, from the members load, a single-OU rehydration N+1 when the entity cache was cold, and commit-time dirty-checking of the hydrated entities (~2GB allocated per request). Measured floor on a large production instance dropped from ~5.2s to ~0.2s.\n\nResolve the count with a count subquery instead: new OrganisationUnitGroupStore.getOrganisationUnitGroupMemberCounts(uids) uses HQL size(g.members), which never initialises the collection; substituteIndicatorExpressions looks up only the referenced groups and substitutes counts directly.\n\nAlso mark substituteIndicatorExpressions @Transactional(readOnly = true): it only mutates the transient Indicator.exploded* display fields, so it never writes; readOnly sets flush mode MANUAL as a guard against dirty-checking.\n\nBehaviour preserved: the count is the global group membership total, as before. The runtime, org-unit-scoped OUG{} count used in analytics is a separate path via orgUnitCountMap.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"90f207d397ab032c676106230d6901c4ddf1dddc","tree_id":"b01f58653680085f60b84380aae1c4b8f4340952","timestamp":"2026-06-19T17:52:26Z","committer":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin